            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p> Welcome to Crave  It – the restaurant with a name as unforgettable as our food! We believe dining should be equal parts flavor and fun. Here, every dish comes with a story: Bhavani might have singed it with passion, but Lavanya makes sure it reaches your table with love (and maybe a little sarcasm too!).

                Our menu blends homely comfort with bold twists, offering something for every mood – from a quick bite to a slow, hearty meal. Whether you’re laughing with friends, celebrating with family, or just craving a dish that feels special, we’ve got you covered.

                At Bhavani Burnt It, Lavanya Served It, food is not just cooked – it’s created with personality. Come hungry, leave happy (and probably with a story to tell).</p>
